    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="1"><![CDATA[The Example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>Use <em>ComboBox </em>to select&nbsp;one of&nbsp;three&nbsp;themes available&nbsp;for <strong><em>Chart </em></strong>control.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="1"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p><strong>Chart.Theme </strong>property gets or sets the theme for <em>Chart </em>control.<br />Property Type: Gizmox.WebGUI.Forms.Charts.ThemeTypes<br />DefaultValue - Gizmox.WebGUI.Forms.Charts.ThemeTypes.<strong>Theme1</strong></p>]]></Paragraph>
